---
/**
 * Privacy Policy
 * How Woorkeasy handles your data and privacy.
 */
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Woorkeasy"
  description="Woorkeasy privacy policy: all tools run client-side, no data upload, no tracking, no cookies. Your files never leave your device."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-xl text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="body-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-4">Last updated: June 2025</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="space-y-8 body-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Our Privacy Promise</h2>
        <p>Woorkeasy is designed with your privacy first. Every tool on this website runs entirely in your browser using client-side processing (JavaScript). Your files, data, and content are never uploaded to any server. We have no access to your files, and we do not store, process, or transmit any user files on our infrastructure.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Data Collection</h2>
        <p>Woorkeasy does not collect, store, or process any personal data. We do not use tracking cookies, analytics scripts, or third-party data collectors. We do not create user profiles, track your browsing behavior, or share any information with advertisers or data brokers.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">The website may serve advertisements via Google AdSense, which may use cookies for ad personalization. This is governed by Google's privacy policy and can be managed through your Google ad settings.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">File Processing</h2>
        <p>All file processing is performed locally on your device using JavaScript. Your files are read, processed, and downloaded from your browser without any data transmission to external servers. Once you close or refresh the page, all processed data is cleared from memory.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>Woorkeasy does not set any first-party cookies. Third-party cookies may be set by Google AdSense for ad personalization, which you can control through your browser settings or Google's ad preferences page.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our website displays advertisements through Google AdSense. Google may use cookies and web beacons to serve personalized ads based on your visits to this and other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google Ad Settings</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:woorkeasy@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">woorkeasy@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
